<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Engineering</title>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- Link to Poppins font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        body, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, p, label, input, select, button {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
        }
        
        .main-content {
            padding: 26px;
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .page-title {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a237e;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        }
        
        .section-description p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #455a64;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .cards-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 32px;
        }
        
        .menu-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 13px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.05);
        }
        
        .menu-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.15);
        }
        
        .card-body {
            padding: 24px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .card-body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.05) 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 70%);
            z-index: -1;
        }
        
        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a237e;
        }
        
        .card-text {
            color: #455a64;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .card-icon {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3d5afe, #304ffe);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 3px rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.3));
        }
        
        .menu-card:nth-child(4n+1) .card-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3d5afe, #304ffe);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .menu-card:nth-child(4n+2) .card-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #00b0ff, #0091ea);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .menu-card:nth-child(4n+3) .card-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #651fff, #6200ea);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .menu-card:nth-child(4n+4) .card-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #2979ff, #2962ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .card-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 19px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3d5afe, #304ffe);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            text-align: center;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.2);
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
        }
        
        .menu-card:nth-child(4n+1) .card-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3d5afe, #304ffe);
        }
        
        .menu-card:nth-child(4n+2) .card-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #00b0ff, #0091ea);
        }
        
        .menu-card:nth-child(4n+3) .card-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #651fff, #6200ea);
        }
        
        .menu-card:nth-child(4n+4) .card-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #2979ff, #2962ff);
        }
        
        .card-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.3);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .section-description {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 13px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 13px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<%- include('../shared/components/header') %>

<div class="main-content">
    <div class="section-description">
        <h1 class="page-title">Engineering</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the Engineering Module. Select one of the options below to manage product development, designs, and technical specifications.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cards-container">
        <div class="menu-card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Product Design</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Create and manage product designs, technical drawings and 3D models.</p>
                <a href="/page/engineering/designs" class="card-btn">Manage Designs</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="menu-card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Bill of Materials</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Manage product components, materials specifications and assembly structures.</p>
                <a href="/page/engineering/bom" class="card-btn">Manage BOMs</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="menu-card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-tasks"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Work Instructions</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Create and manage assembly instructions, manufacturing procedures and quality standards.</p>
                <a href="/page/engineering/instructions" class="card-btn">Manage Instructions</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="menu-card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Technical Documents</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Manage technical specifications, certification documents and compliance records.</p>
                <a href="/page/engineering/documents" class="card-btn">Manage Documents</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="menu-card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Engineering Change</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Manage engineering change orders, track revisions and implement design modifications.</p>
                <a href="/page/engineering/change-management" class="card-btn">Manage Changes</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="menu-card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Process Planning</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Design and optimize manufacturing processes, create routing instructions and production workflows.</p>
                <a href="/page/engineering/processes" class="card-btn">Manage Processes</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="menu-card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-microscope"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Quality Control</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Define quality standards, inspection procedures and testing protocols.</p>
                <a href="/page/engineering/quality" class="card-btn">Manage QC</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="menu-card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">R&D Projects</h3>
                <p class="card-text">Manage research projects, track development milestones and document innovations.</p>
                <a href="/page/engineering/projects" class="card-btn">Manage Projects</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Bootstrap Scripts -->
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
